Title: 'Science travel and '
DateModified: '2019-02-24'
DatePublished: '2019-02-24'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/science-travel-and
SetInCountry: Turkey
Category: Making a local connection
AuthorName: Beshta Azizi
AuthorCountry: Afghanistan
Text: "My trip was through a university and institute of the Yusous Imra of a thousand\
  \ students from one hundred and ten countries around the world.\nMy trip had two\
  \ parts:  studying 60 hours Turkish language and traveling around the Turkey. In\
  \ addition to 60 hours of Turkish language, we also had cultural and artistic activities.\n\
  Cultural activities: visiting the museums participating in cultural clothes shows\
  \ and introduction of Turkish cultural.\nArtistic activities: painting, playing\
  \ guitar and other Local musical instruments and other activities like horse riding\
  \ and swimming.  \nEvery Saturday and Sunday we traveled to other Turkish cities\
  \ to visit the ancient places and nature of Turkey on the sunny days we had boat\
  \ trip from morning to evening and swimming on the black sea I enjoyed so much and\
  \ I had fantastic memory.\nThat was my best travel experience."
